# Boas referências para começar a estudar o shiny

O link a seguir é o primeiro site que você deveria estudar http://shiny.rstudio.com/tutorial/

Outros links interessantes são

- https://www.rstudio.com/resources/webinars/how-to-start-with-shiny-part-1/
- http://rstudio.github.io/shinythemes e 
- https://github.com/rstudio/shiny-examples
- http://www.lisa.stat.vt.edu/?q=node/7934
- http://www.htmlwidgets.org/
- http://www.showmeshiny.com/
- http://shinyapps.org/
- https://www.rstudio.com/products/shiny/shiny-user-showcase/
- http://rcharts.io/gallery/

